criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  participants are apparently healthy and recreationally active males between the ages
             of 18 and 40;

          -  participants will need to have at least six months immediate prior history of
             resistance training on the bench press and leg press or squat;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  participants have a history of treatment for metabolic disease (i.e., diabetes),
             hypertension, hypotension, thyroid disease, arrhythmias and/or cardiovascular disease;

          -  participants are currently using prescription medications;

          -  participants have a history of smoking;

          -  participants drink excessively (i.e., 12 drinks per week or more);

          -  participants have a recent history of creatine supplementation within six weeks of the
             start of supplementation;
